00:05:22,544 --> 00:05:25,845
because I'm not a lawyer, but I do...

148
00:05:27,348 --> 00:05:28,415
Because I am.

149
00:05:28,450 --> 00:05:30,216
Okay, you've had your fun.

150
00:05:30,251 --> 00:05:31,651
Now I'm gonna have mine.

151
00:05:31,686 --> 00:05:34,320
Your lawyer actually did
show up about half hour ago.

152
00:05:34,355 --> 00:05:36,155
There seemed to be a
little miscommunication

153
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,557
about what room you were in,

